import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import vuetify from './plugins/vuetify'
import '@babel/polyfill'
import { functions } from '@/func.js'

Vue.config.productionTip = false
Vue.prototype.$func = functions

new Vue({
  router,
  vuetify,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
